Class IsoFile

java.lang.Object
  com.googlecode.mp4parser.AbstractBox
      com.googlecode.mp4parser.AbstractContainerBox
          com.coremedia.iso.IsoFile
All Implemented Interfaces:
Box, ContainerBox
@DoNotParseDetail
public class IsoFile
extends AbstractContainerBox

The most upper container for ISO Boxes. It is a container box that is a file. Uses IsoBufferWrapper to access the underlying file.
